Description: This statistical release makes available the most recent Improving Access to Psychological Therapies (IAPT) monthly data, including activity, waiting times, and outcomes such as recovery.
Name: Psychological Therapies: reports on the use of IAPT services, England June 2019 final including reports on the IAPT pilots and Quarter data
Notes: This release also includes experimental statistics from the IAPT integrated health pilot and the IAPT Employment Adviser pilot.
Route from landing page to data: Data on this page identified via a link at top of page under heading Summary then Latest version. This will link to another page with the latest data, identified on page under heading Resources as a series of tables in XLS and CSV format.
Sizing Notes: Large mutiple dimensions CSV files contains mothnly activity data but additional data included in other XLS files with messy tables, dimensions and footmotes.
